{
  "id": "adv_card_szk_08_02",
  "title": "兵藤雫 2話 サバイバルのイメトレ",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――無人島ロケからしばらく経った頃",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Some time after the deserted island shoot",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "よし、雫。次の現場まではタクシーで……うん？\nどうしたんだ、空を見上げて？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright‚ Shizuku. We'll take a taxi to the next location… hmm?\nWhat's wrong? Why are you looking up at the sky?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 10.2333332896
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_02-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "昨日は綺麗な夕焼けだったから……今日はよく晴れてる\n予想、的中……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Since yesterday’s sunset was beautiful… today’s weather is really clear.\nCorrect prediction…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 17.3333332896
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "昨日は夕焼け……言われてみればそうだったかもな\nでも、天気予報を見れば済むことだろ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sunset yesterday… now that you mention it‚ that might be true.\nBut you could just check the weather forecast‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_02-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん……\n違う、そういうことじゃない……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san…\nNo‚ that's not the point…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 30.2333332896
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_02-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "日頃から空の情報を読み取って、天気を予想出来るよう\nにならないと……いざという時に生き残れない……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You need to be able to read the sky and predict weather everyday\nor you won't be able to survive in an emergency…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 38.3666666229
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "そこまで危機感を持って過ごしてるのか……\nす……凄いな、雫は",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're living with that much sense of crisis…\nThat's… amazing‚ Shizuku.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 44.7666666229
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_02-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "これくらいはまだまだ初歩的……\n引き続き精進する所存……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This is still just elementary…\nI intend to continue training…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（雫が普段アイドルに向けてる興味が、思いきり）\n（サバイバルに向けられてるんだな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（The interest Shizuku usually has for idols）\n（is now completely aimed at survival.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.2333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-camera-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6700.001061000002,
          "startTime": 56.3666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 53.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 57.0999958872
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "……ん？\n雫？　なんで道端の草の写真を撮ってるんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Hmm?\nShizuku? Why are you taking pictures of roadside grass?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.0333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-camera-01.m4a",
          "delay": 620.0041127999966,
          "startTime": 57.72
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6933.3333333999935,
          "startTime": 64.9666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 62.2333292205
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_02-szk005.m4a",
      "text": "草じゃない……これは野草……\nよし、送信完了",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's not grass… this is wild vegetation…\nAlright‚ sending complete.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 68.0666666228
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_02-szk006.m4a",
      "text": "すみれちゃんと野草とかサバイバル知識の話で\n盛り上がって……メッセグループを作った",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sumire-chan and I got excited talking about wild plants and\nsurvival knowledge… so we made a message group.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.6666646321,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 75.1999989389
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_02-szk007.m4a",
      "text": "franさんも無人島で遭難したって噂を聞いてたから\nすみれちゃんと一緒に誘って、なんとか入ってもらった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I heard rumors that fran-san was also stranded on a deserted island‚\nso Sumire-chan and I invited her together and somehow got her to join.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.5666636149,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 83.6666656056
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "な、なんとも不思議なメンバーだな\n雫にすみれ、そこにfranさんか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-What a strange group of members.\nShizuku‚ Sumire‚ and fran-san…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.8999969482,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_02-szk008.m4a",
      "text": "といっても、franさんは「勝手にやれば」っていう\nスタンス……ブレないところがかっこいい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Though fran-san has a \"do whatever you want\" stance…\nher unwavering attitude is cool.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.1666636149,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 99.0666656056
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_02-szk009.m4a",
      "text": "私が野草の写真を無言で送ると、franさんが\n十回に一回くらいの確率で名前を答えてくれる……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When I silently send wild plant photos‚ fran-san\nanswers with the name about once every ten times…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.3666636149,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_02-szk010.m4a",
      "text": "そこにすみれちゃんが野草の調理方法を\n追加説明してくれるのが黄金パターン……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then Sumire-chan adds cooking methods\nfor the wild plant that's the golden pattern…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.7333358764,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 115.3000030079
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "無人島のロケ前なら\n絶対に予想出来ない会話内容だな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Before the deserted island shoot‚\nthis would be absolutely unpredictable conversation…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.8999964396,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_02-szk011.m4a",
      "text": "franさんはあくまで楽屋で暇な時にだけ答えて\nくれる……でも、答えてもらえると、とっても嬉しい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "fran-san only answers when she's bored in the dressing room…\nbut when she does answer‚ I'm really happy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.9333297729,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_02-szk012.m4a",
      "text": "私とすみれちゃんが喜ぶたびに「百円ね」って要求\nされるけど、一回ちゃんと課金しようかと思ってる……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Every time Sumire-chan and I get happy‚ she demands \"100 yen.\"\nI'm honestly thinking of paying once…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.2666631062,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 137.4333322722
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "いやいやいや、franさんの要求はさすがに冗談だと\n思うぞ？　そんな真剣に考えなくていいから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No no no‚ I think fran-san's demands are obviously jokes.\nYou don't need to think about it so seriously.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.3333297729,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 143.8999735076
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_02-szk013.m4a",
      "text": "そう……なの？\nでも、推し活するのは、ドルオタの使命だから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is that… so?\nBut supporting your favorites is an idol otaku's mission…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.7666478474,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "言いたいことは分かるが、星見プロのアイドルの中で\n使命がどうこうは考えなくていいから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I understand what you want to say‚ but among Hoshimi Pro idols‚\nyou don't need to think about missions!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.1333216349,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5433.344014499994,
          "startTime": 158.5666656494
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 6200.010681200012,
          "startTime": 159.3333323161
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
