    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_02-szk014.m4a",
      "text": "あ、{user}さん……おはようございます\n私……悟りを得た",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ {user}-san… good morning.\nI… have achieved enlightenment.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 164.8999969482,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_02-szk015.m4a",
      "text": "サバイバルは――ナイフに始まり、ナイフに終わる\nふん、ふん、ふん……っ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Survival― begins with a knife and ends with a knife.\nHmph‚ hmph‚ hmph…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 171.933328247,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4400.007164500011,
          "startTime": 171.9666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5233.3354115000075,
          "startTime": 172.7999949137
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5633.335411500013,
          "startTime": 173.1999949137
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4766.664632100003,
          "startTime": 176.6999928791
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "えぇと……雫？　何をしてるんだ？　素振り……？\n何も持ってないようだけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um… Shizuku? What are you doing? Practicing swings…?\nYou don't seem to be holding anything…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 180.5333262125,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_02-szk016.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さんと話した時「結局シンプルな刃物が\nサバイバルに一番必要だよね」って聞いて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When I talked with Haruko-san‚ she said\n\"Simple blades are what you need most for survival\"…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 187.2333262125,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_02-szk017.m4a",
      "text": "それで、次の休日に遙子さんとナイフを見に行くん\nだけど……それまではこうしてイメトレをしてる……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So next holiday‚ Haruko-san and I are going to look at knives…\nbut until then‚ I'm doing image training like this…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 195.2666595458,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_02-szk018.m4a",
      "text": "食料確保、いかだ作り……\nナイフの扱いをマスターして生き残る確率を上げる……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mastering food procurement‚ raft building…\nand knife handling to increase survival probability…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 202.3333170572,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "日頃から心がけておくのはいいことだと思うが……\nそろそろ現場に向かう時間だぞ？　準備はいいのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think it's good to keep it in mind daily‚ but…\nIt's almost time to head to the location. Are you ready?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 210.6333170572,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_02-szk019.m4a",
      "text": "え、時間……？　……はっ！\nご、ごご、ご、ごめんなさい……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh‚ time…? …Ah!\nS-s-s-sorry…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 217.0999837238,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_02-szk020.m4a",
      "text": "夢中になって、次のお仕事のこと\nすっかり忘れてた……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I got so absorbed that I completely forgot\nabout the next job…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 221.9999837238,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_02-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "慌てなくて大丈夫だよ。まぁ……何かに夢中になるのは\nいいことだが、あくまで適度にな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don't panic‚ it's okay. Well… getting absorbed in\nsomething is good‚ but in moderation.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 228.5666503905,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_02-szk021.m4a",
      "text": "はい……ごめんなさい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes… I'm sorry.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 231.6666422088,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_02-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "それにしても、雫がここまでハマるなんてな\n俺もちょっと驚いてるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Still‚ I'm surprised that Shizuku would get this into it.\nI'm a bit surprised too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 239.0999766031,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_02-szk022.m4a",
      "text": "その……無人島のサバイバルが\n本当にいい思い出になった、から……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well… the deserted island survival\nbecame such a good memory…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 244.6666432697,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_02-szk023.m4a",
      "text": "私……林間学校とか、そういう学校の行事\nあんまり参加したことなくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I… never really participated in school events\nlike summer camp and such…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 252.6666330972,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_02-szk024.m4a",
      "text": "『ぱじゃパ！』の時みたいに\nみんなでわいわいするのが、本当に楽しくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Like during \"Pajama Party!\"\nhaving fun with everyone was really enjoyable…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 257.3333129881,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_02-szk025.m4a",
      "text": "でも、だからって、仕事に影響が出て\n迷惑を掛けちゃうのは違う……ごめんなさい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But that doesn't mean it should affect work\nand cause trouble… I'm sorry.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 264.2666330972,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_02-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "反省してくれるならそれでいいよ\n程良く楽しむ分には構わないから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you're reflecting on it‚ that's fine.\nIt's okay to enjoy it in moderation.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 271.0999664305,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-call-01.m4a",
          "delay": 10733.333333300037,
          "startTime": 281.8332997638
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_02-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "（……とは言ったものの、かなり落ち込んでるな）\n（どうしたものか……ん？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（…Though I said that‚ she's quite down）\n（What should I do… hmm?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 280.3666330972,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_02-szk026.m4a",
      "text": "電話……なんの話だったの？\n私のこと、チラチラ見てたような……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The phone call… what was it about?\nYou seemed to be glancing at me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 289.3999664305,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_02-koh016.m4a",
      "text": "無人島脱出番組が雑誌で特集を組まれることになってな\n付録のポスター撮影をあの無人島で行いたいそうだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The deserted island escape show is going to be featured in a magazine.\nThey want to do a poster shoot for the appendix on that deserted island.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 297.999980672,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_02-koh017.m4a",
      "text": "撮影スケジュールを見たところ、サニピメンバーで\nその日に空いているのは雫だけなんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Looking at the shooting schedule‚ among Sunny Peace members‚\nonly you are free that day.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 304.9666473387,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_02-szk027.m4a",
      "text": "参加出来るのが、私だけ……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Only I can participate…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 307.8333149789,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_02-koh018.m4a",
      "text": "仕事でなら、思う存分サバイバル好きを\n発揮してくれていいぞ。どうだ、やってみないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If it's for work‚ you can fully display\nyour love of survival. How about it? Want to try?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 314.0999664305,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_02-szk028.m4a",
      "text": "やりたい……！　お願いします！\nいい仕事出来るよう、頑張る……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want to do it…! Please!\nI'll work hard to do a good job…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 321.0666330972,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}